sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User
  participant UI as Frontend UI
  participant API as Flask API
  participant DB as migration.db

  User->>UI: Open app and choose species
  UI->>API: GET /api/species?limit=200
  API->>DB: Query species + counts
  DB-->>API: Species rows
  API-->>UI: JSON species payload

  UI->>API: GET /api/visualization/?species_code=eurcur
  API->>DB: Query weekly aggregates
  DB-->>API: Weekly rows
  API->>DB: Query route points
  DB-->>API: Route rows
  API-->>UI: Weekly + route_points + timeline_weeks

  UI-->>User: Render map and weekly chart
